title: Football Focus - 16th May 2015 - hdtv x264
description:
SPORT: Football Focus
On: BBC 1 HD  
Date: Saturday 16th May 2015 
Time: 12:10 to 12:50 

Jason Mohammad and guests look ahead to the weekend's football action. It's the penultimate weekend of the Premier League season, so there's plenty at stake for clubs at both the top and the bottom of the table. There are seven Saturday matches in the top flight and Sunday's intriguing clash at Old Trafford between Manchester United and Arsenal to look forward to. Also featuring a round-up of all the action from the play-offs in the Football League.
